14:["$","p","12",{"className":"text-[#B3B3B3] leading-relaxed my-3","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"The Xone:92 is the benchmark for serious vinyl DJing — used in clubs worldwide for over 20 years. Its analog filter section, 6-band resonant filters, and exceptionally clean phono preamps make it the choice of house and techno DJs globally."}}]
