3a:["$","p","50",{"className":"text-[#B3B3B3] leading-relaxed my-3","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"For vinyl DJs, the mixer is a long-term investment. Buy the best phono preamps you can afford — they directly affect how your records sound. The Allen & Heath Xone:92 remains the gold standard, but Pioneer and Rane offer excellent alternatives depending on your genre and playing style. Start with a decent budget option and upgrade when you outgrow it."}}]
